i tried the player rights thing that dident work[/quote]
Go to Client Typ Ctrl + F Then Search For ThiefStall

Then you can see this :
if(objectID == 2562){
ThiefStall(“gem stall”, “and recieve 100M”, 80, 700*playerLevel[17], 995, 100000000, 0x340);

Edit this 995, 100000000, 0x340)
Thats the Amount
